{"tid":618574,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《再見螢火蟲》導演高畑勳逝世，終年82歲","createTime":"2018-04-06T02:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T03:51:27.000Z","uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f18ed4343d12a4aa8c6f946e6d8d6fc3aa9ebf0","tid":618574,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"執導《再見螢火蟲》、《飄零燕》等多部知名影片的日本動畫大師高畑勳昨天(5日)在東京都內醫院去世，享年82歲。<br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報道，高畑勳去年夏天開始身體狀況轉差，傳出有心臟疾病，昨日在東京的醫院逝世。高畑勳1965年與宮崎駿及大塚康生合作，耗費3年執導完成個人第一部劇院電影動畫《太陽王子 霍爾斯的大冒險》。1985年高畑勳、宮崎駿成立後來舉世聞名的「吉卜力工作室」。<br />\n<br />\n高畑勳首次在吉卜力推出的動畫為1988年的《再見螢火蟲》，隨後則依序執導了《歲月的童話》、《百變狸貓》、《隔壁的山田君》等吉卜力動畫，《輝耀姬物語》則是他最後的一部作品，並獲得2014年奧斯卡最佳動畫的提名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caf810c37ad956c644011fbd44158fe312b9d8a","tid":618574,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.karousell.com/media/photos/products/2017/11/21/____1511199462_3b2d792d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.karousell.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fproducts%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F____1511199462_3b2d792d.jpg&h=5ecac718&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e574056a6aba4cc01809867080ca4e1ea24fdb5c","tid":618574,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8caf810c37ad956c644011fbd44158fe312b9d8a","tid":618574,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.karousell.com/media/photos/products/2017/11/21/____1511199462_3b2d792d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.karousell.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fproducts%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F____1511199462_3b2d792d.jpg&h=5ecac718&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"果汁糖骨灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600fa6a94a58550a1995457644b66253c2c8c42d","tid":618574,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"再見螢火蟲睇到喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f54560ce6683b042b7a6c08c2a3e6c9f671ade","tid":618574,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"人生睇一次就夠，你老味一撚定會流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c06a4895ab7ea927bbabbb74d1bc2f2bfbd4996","tid":618574,"uid":34777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人生睇一次就夠，你老味一撚定會流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n次次一唔開心就會睇再見螢火蟲用嚟發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇親都喊到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1874b1dcca8dc97b2f3f72f91bf834411cddbf2","tid":618574,"uid":101699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a9cd70f9cf246079ca00441101eb3d4793e298","tid":618574,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"希望佢快啲係天堂搵到妹妹 彌補佢以前嘅遺憾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb1a689735e90bbf61c1b1fcc86651f6f8d2e17","tid":618574,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"時代既巨輪又開始轉動，好快吉卜力老野都死晒&hellip;"},{"pid":"f9e9cfb46719059906fdaa576fbe2f84d75ecd2f","tid":618574,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dis